author: Divya Rao
title: Kareena Kapoor’s Nickname For Taimur Ali Khan Is As Unique As His Real Name
text:
A post shared by Kareena Kapoor Khan FC (@kareenakapoorteam) on Feb 12, 2017 at 8:06am PST 
Kareena Kapoor and Saif Ali Khan brought into this world their bundle of joy, Taimur Ali Khan , a couple of months ago, and the world got way too excited. We showed this uber cute photo of Taimur that Saif had as his Whatsapp DP and man, does he look just like Kareena! While the world has lots of things to say about his name , Kareena has given her son this unique nickname. 
According to a report in TOI, Bebo calls her son “Little John”. We’re not quite sure why but her friends too have reportedly started calling this adorable boy by the same name! Lol. Trust Bebo to come up with something as unique as “Little John” for her son. 7
